Cold Borscht

45 min
$8.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

Chilled SoupHealthyEasy to Prepare

Description

A refreshing and vibrant chilled beet soup, perfect for hot days and packed with nutrients!

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 large, boiled and peeled
  • cucumbers: 1, diced
  • plain yogurt: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • red onion: 1/2, finely chopped
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
